                  <p>
                     <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178410200101"></xptr>THE WHOLE PROCEEDINGS ON THE KING's Commission of the Peace, Oyer and Terminer, and Gaol Delivery for the CITY of LONDON; AND ALSO The Gaol Delivery for the County of Middlesex; HELD AT JUSTICE HALL in the OLD BAILEY, On Wednesday the 20th of OCTOBER, 1784, and the following Days;</p>
                  <p>Being the EIGHTH SESSION in the Mayoralty of The Right Hon. 
                  <persName id="t17841020-63-person631">
                     ROBERT
                      PECKHAM
                  <interp inst="t17841020-63-person631" type="surname" value="PECKHAM"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17841020-63-person631" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17841020-63-person631" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
               , Esq; 
                  <persName id="t17841020-63-person632">
                     LORD
                      MAYOR
                  <interp inst="t17841020-63-person632" type="surname" value="MAYOR"></interp>
